AUSTRALIA
<http://www.daff.gov.au/>
[The increase in the number of cases is somewhat to be expected at
this point in the control/eradication attempts. Although this update
mentions wind movement, it is more often associated with close
contact. There are continued media reports of violation of the
stand-still order -- this seems a more likely method of spread.
However, mutation of the virus may allow for airborne spread. - Mod.TG]
